{"tid":1771681,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"法國戰線機會來了（徵法文巴絲）","createTime":"2019-12-06T04:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T06:57:18.000Z","uid":304769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"801c6505c549150a04cf220ec79a74c0bbd99f5f","tid":1771681,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:50:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家有跟開國際戰線都知道：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">全球領袖宜家都割席支共，北約之中唯獨法國總統同德國總理唔割。</span><br />\n宜家法國爆發大罷工，其中一點就係<span style=\"color: red;\">不信任總統以及不信任政府</span>。<br />\n所以，我地要嚮國際線<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏法國網民，多宣傳支那貨品同勞工入侵破壞歐洲經濟，以及支那不良價值觀入侵，強調&ldquo;法國總統不代表我（法國人）&rdquo;，進一步connect法國。拉攏法國人採取更右翼更反共立場，利用民意迫使法國政府加入反共陣營，進一步圍堵支共</span>，大家點睇？<br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"d3461786f4e086afeb1c114c88e2cc4e6f41149c","tid":1771681,"uid":293417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T06:05:49.000Z","msg":"支持。<br />\n利申：法文B2左右，住過巴黎三個月"},{"pid":"b63909317727bca2b2fcd36395b3d469f7f69651","tid":1771681,"uid":293417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T06:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/79116708_1457832984380393_5985256438459531264_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ohc=Yzf98IPEB0QAQmZEuL5JETXoTAnIidiZpUQD8i11eNiuEW39n-VFgyfIA&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=07ed5f1407b790c23d1491790052f590&amp;oe=5E8B7A5F\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F79116708_1457832984380393_5985256438459531264_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ohc%3DYzf98IPEB0QAQmZEuL5JETXoTAnIidiZpUQD8i11eNiuEW39n-VFgyfIA%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3D07ed5f1407b790c23d1491790052f590%26oe%3D5E8B7A5F&h=2852c534&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/79293729_1457832987713726_380121716845707264_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ohc=JPLl3ipPTuQAQnzdsvgszk2DgvU0aVO32MXMLf7ECdT1SnvHmEIyqsb-w&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&am